float GET_INTERIOR_HEADING(int interior);Parameters:interior: ID of the interiorReturns: Returns interior heading in radians. Multiply the returned value with 57.29578 (or 180.0 / math.pi) to convert it to degrees.NativeDB Introduced: v1493Old name:  _GET_INTERIOR_HEADING
